name: label-maker
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9.1" %}

package:
  name: label-maker
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/l/label-maker/label-maker-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: e0a3d9198ca29cb9b2ebf8d6645c0ff7848d42333f974b1b2ee3976ced33af4f

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 1
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv
  entry_points:
    - label-maker=label_maker.main:cli

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - pip
  run:
    - python
    - numpy >=1.13.3
    - cerberus >=1.1
    - click >=6.7
    - geojson >=2.3.0
    - homura >=0.1.5
    - humanize >=0.5.1
    - mercantile >=1.0.0
    - olefile >=0.44
    - pillow >=4.3.0
    - protobuf >=3.5.0.post1
    - pyclipper >=1.0.6
    - pycurl >=7.43.0.1
    - pyproj >=1.9.5.1
    - rasterio >=1.0a12
    - requests >=2.20.0
    - shapely >=1.6.3
    - six >=1.10.0
    - mapbox-vector-tile >=1.2.0
    - mbutil >=0.3.0
    - tilepie >=0.2.1
    - tqdm

test:
  imports:
    - label_maker
  commands:
    - label-maker --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/developmentseed/label-maker/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Data preparation for satellite machine learning
  dev_url: https://github.com/developmentseed/label-maker

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - mxr-conda
    - rluria14
    - benhuff
    - oblute
